---
title: Chicken Schnitzel & Pear-Parmesan Salad with Garlic Aioli
description: It's easy to whip up a classic schnitzel at home, and we're going to show you how! Then, make it a meal with a sweet and savoury salad, studded with pear and Parmesan cheese, plus some garlic aioli for dipping. Delicious!
